- Add steps selection
- Add read group option
- Add check for no arguments
- Add version file
- Fix default steps array
- Move quantDir initalization before it's accessed
- Fix removal of flux gtf file
- Fix sort command for unstranded data in contigs step
- Update exon quantification file name
- Change bigwig files extension
- Change umask for group write permissions
- Update to scripts v1.2
- Fix pipeline bins version
- Fixed pysam package version in python requirements
- Fixed typo in read-group option help
- Update name for exon quantifications file when using temp dir
- Umask applies to the shell spawn by the script
- Add help message for STEPS

